title: AWS re:Invent 2025 - Migration & Modernization: How AWS Partners help customers transform (PEX109)
title_cn: AWS re:Invent 2025 - 迁移与现代化：AWS 合作伙伴如何帮助客户实现转型 (PEX109)
abstract: Hear how AWS Partners are making impact supporting customers on their digital transformation journeys. This session highlights customer success stories where partners have used AWS Partner Programs to accelerate change.
abstract_cn: 了解AWS合作伙伴如何在支持客户数字化转型旅程中产生影响。本次会议重点介绍客户成功案例，展示合作伙伴如何利用AWS合作伙伴计划加速变革。
